&lt;h4&gt;AI Interaction&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p id="ai-instructions"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id="participant-advisor-ai-client" style="display: none;"&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Your role: Energy Advisor. The AI is your client.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Explain one of your plans to the AI client and try to convince them to adopt it. Enter your explanation below:&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;textarea id="advisor-input" rows="5" style="width: 90%;"&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;br&gt;
  &lt;button onclick="interactWithAI('adviseClient')"&gt;Send Advice to AI Client&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Client Response:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;pre id="ai-client-response" style="white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc;"&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div id="ai-client-ai-planner" style="display: none;"&gt;
   &lt;p&gt;The AI is acting as both a Client and a Planner.&lt;/p&gt;
   &lt;p&gt;Below is a plan generated by an AI Planner for the same goal.&lt;/p&gt;
   &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Planner's Plan:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
