   &lt;br&gt;
   &lt;p&gt;You can now:&lt;/p&gt;
   &lt;button onclick="interactWithAI('comparePlan')"&gt;Compare your Plan 1 with AI Plan&lt;/button&gt;
   &lt;button onclick="interactWithAI('getAdvice')"&gt;Ask AI Planner for Advice on Your Plan 1&lt;/button&gt;
